#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:-1
msgid "digiKam Geolocation Settings"
msgstr "Nastavenia geolokácie digiKam"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:-1
msgid ""
"digiKam, documentation, user manual, photo management, open source, free, "
"learn, easy, geolocation, map"
msgstr ""
"digiKam, dokumentácia, používateľský manuál, správa fotografii, open source, "
"slobodný, učiť sa, jednoduchý, geolokácia, mapa"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:14
msgid ":ref:`Geolocation Settings <setup_application>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Nastavenia geolokácie <setup_application>`"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:16
msgid "Contents"
msgstr "Obsah"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:18
msgid ""
"The **Geolocation** options for digiKam are set from :menuselection:"
"`Settings --> Configure digiKam... --> Geolocation page`. These settings "
"control the multiple map views within digiKam."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti **Geolokácie** pre digiKam sa nastavujú cez :menuselection:"
"`Nastavenia --> Nakonfigurovať digiKam... --> stránka Geolokácia`. Tieto "
"nastavenia riadia viaceremé zobrazenia máp v rámci digiKam."

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:23
msgid "Map View Settings"
msgstr "Nastavenia zobrazenia mapy"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:25
msgid ""
"The **Map View** tab allows you to control the displays and behaviors within "
"the digiKam map views."
msgstr ""
"Karta **Zobrazenie mapy** umožňuje ovládať zobrazenie a správanie v "
"zobrazeniach mapy digiKam."

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:31
msgid "The digiKam Geolocation Map View Settings Page"
msgstr "Stránka nastavenia zobrazenia mapy geolokácie digiKam"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:35
msgid "Units"
msgstr "Jednotky"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:35
msgid ""
"**Distance** sets the distance units (km, miles, nautical miles) used in the "
"map displays."
msgstr ""
"**Vzdialenosť** nastavuje jednotky vzdialenosti (km, míle, námorné míle) "
"používané v zobrazeniach mapy."

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:36
msgid ""
"**Angle** set the angle units (decimal degrees, DMS, UTM) used in the map "
"displays."
msgstr ""
"**Uhol** nastavuje jednotky uhla (desiatkové stupne, DMS, UTM) používané v "
"zobrazeniach mapy."

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:38
msgid "Map Quality"
msgstr "Kvalita mapy"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:38
msgid ""
"**Still Image** sets the quality (resolution) of the map display when the "
"display is still."
msgstr ""
"**Statický obrázok** nastavuje kvalitu (rozlíšenie) zobrazenia mapy, keď je "
"zobrazenie v pokoji."

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:39
msgid ""
"**During Animations** sets the quality (resolution) of the map display when "
"during animations. Higher quality will be slower."
msgstr ""
"**Počas animácií** nastavuje kvalitu (rozlíšenie) zobrazenia mapy počas "
"animácií. Vyššia kvalita bude pomalejšia."

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:41
msgid "Mouse Behavior"
msgstr "Správanie myši"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:41
msgid "**Inertial Globe Rotation**"
msgstr "**Zotrvačná rotácia glóbusu**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:42
msgid "**View Rotation**"
msgstr "**Otočenie zobrazenia**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:44
msgid "Cache"
msgstr "Vyrovnávacia pamäť"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:44
msgid "**Physical Memory**"
msgstr "**Fyzická pamäť**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:45
msgid "**Hard Disc**"
msgstr "**Pevný disk**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:47
msgid "**Show Coordinate Grid**"
msgstr "**Zobraziť súradnicovú sieť**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:48
msgid "**Show Cross-Hair**"
msgstr "**Zobraziť nitkový kríž**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:49
msgid "**Show Atmospheric Glow**"
msgstr "**Zobraziť atmosferický svit**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:50
msgid "**Show Night Shadow**"
msgstr "**Zobraziť nočný tieň**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:51
msgid "**Show City Place Mark**"
msgstr "**Zobraziť značky miest**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:52
msgid "**Show Relief**"
msgstr "**Zobraziť reliéf**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:53
msgid "** Default Font**"
msgstr "** Predvolené písmo**"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:54
msgid "The options that can be set in this page include:"
msgstr "Možnosti, ktoré možno nastaviť na tejto stránke, zahrňajú:"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:54
msgid "Map Contents"
msgstr "Obsah mapy"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:59
msgid "Map Plugins Settings"
msgstr "Nastavenia zásuvných modulov mapy"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:61
msgid ""
"The **Map Plugins** tab lists all of the map plugins installed in digiKam, "
"and allows the user to toggle on or off those plugins that control map "
"overlays. Settings are also available to further customize some of the "
"overlays."
msgstr ""
"Karta **Zásuvné moduly mapy** zobrazuje zoznam všetkých zásuvných modulov "
"mapy nainštalovaných v digiKam a umožňuje používateľovi zapnúť alebo vypnúť "
"moduly, ktoré riadia vrstvy mapy. K dispozícii sú aj nastavenia na ďalšie "
"prispôsobenie niektorých vrstiev."

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:67
msgid "The digiKam Geolocation Map Plugins Settings Page"
msgstr "Stránka nastavenia zásuvných modulov mapy geolokácie digiKam"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:69
msgid ""
"The map render tools that produce the overlays include: Atmosphere, Compass, "
"Coordinate Grid, Crosshairs, Download Progress Indicator, Measure Tool, "
"Navigation, Overview Map, and a Scale Bar."
msgstr ""
"Nástroje renderovania mapy, ktoré vytvárajú vrstvy, zahrňajú: Atmosféru, "
"Kompas, Sieť súradníc, Krížové značky, Indikátor priebehu stiahnutia, "
"Nástroj merania, Navigáciu, Prehľadovú mapu a Mierovú lídiu."

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:71
msgid "The runner plugins used to parse GPS files are also listed."
msgstr ""
"Sú tu uvedené aj zásuvné moduly spracovateľa používané na analýzu súborov "
"GPS."

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:77
msgid "Google Maps Settings"
msgstr "Nastavenia Google Maps"

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:79
msgid ""
"The **Google Maps** tab allows you to enter an API key to use Google Maps. "
"Google Maps is usable without this key, but will overlay the maps with the "
"words \"For Development Only\". See `this page <https://mapsplatform.google."
"com/pricing/>`_ for more information."
msgstr ""
"Karta **Google Maps** umožňuje zadať kľúč API na používanie Google Maps. "
"Google Maps je použiteľné bez tohto kľúča, ale mapy budou prekryté slovami "
"„Len na vývoj“. Viac informácií nájdete na `tejto stránke <https://"
"mapsplatform.google.com/pricing/>`_."

#: ../../setup_application/geolocation_settings.rst:85
msgid "The digiKam Geolocation Google Map Settings Page"
msgstr "Stránka nastavenia Google Maps geolokácie digiKam"
